{
  "stem": "3475.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Even little-- as I remember, it comes to me now, children in Taylor Tots-- in, you know, in walkers, who were maybe two or three years old, already-- were already calling [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They couldn't say [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They would say [POLISH], you know, like children cannot pronounced the R.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But even the little kids were indoctrinated in this anti-Semitism, unfortunately, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So this was sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because I think that maybe if the Polish people would not be so happy to cooperate with the Nazis, if they would at least close their eyes, many, many more Jews would be left alive, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Even-- don't even talk about hiding out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But just close your eyes, pretend you don't see them, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So they could live their, their own life, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But unfortunately, it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the, the Polish police was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I'll never, never forget, in the ghetto, I saw-- an old lady was selling-- had a basket of bagels to sell.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I guess they had to pay off the, the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And she maybe didn't pay off because he dumped her whole basket of bagels into the ground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he stomped on it, you know, crunched them all up, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "This poor old lady, you know, that's probably all she had in the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So that's coming back and answering your question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was good and bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it was good that we were free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could go wherever we want to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could take the street cart and go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could-- we played soccer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We played volleyball and basketball on the-- on the playgrounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But also what bothered us a lot is that the Germans were living wonderful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They still had their beautiful homes, villas.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
